BMI Calculator 🏋️‍♂️
A simple Body Mass Index (BMI) Calculator built using Python. This script allows users to input their weight and height, then calculates their BMI and categorizes it based on standard BMI classifications.

🚀 Features
✅ User-friendly CLI interface
✅ Supports both Metric (kg, meters) & Imperial (lbs, inches) units
✅ Provides BMI classification (Underweight, Normal, Overweight, Obese)
✅ Error handling for invalid inputs

📊 BMI Categories
BMI Range	Category
< 18.5	Underweight
18.5 – 24.9	Normal Weight
25 – 29.9	Overweight
30+	Obese
🛠️ Technologies Used
Python 3.x

🎯 Future Improvements
Add a GUI version using Tkinter

Web-based version with Flask/Django

Integration with Health APIs for better recommendations
